  "title": "Freelance Sales Executive",
  "description": "<p>Our company is led by a young and passionate team committed to servicing SMEs and Sole Proprietorships. We are looking for a team with the right attitude and experiences, take pride in surpassing our customers’ expectations to apply for the following position.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Main Responsibilities:</p>\n<p>- Cold calling and generate appointments. (B2B)</p>\n<p>- Identify and generate new leads through cold calling, networking, and social media</p>\n<p>- Confident present to decision makers.</p>\n<p>- Develop, build, and manage a client base of corporate accounts.</p>\n<p>- Target new and existing corporate accounts.</p>\n<p>- Prepare and deliver presentations demonstrating Company products and services.</p>\n<p>- Successful on-boarding of new clients.</p>\n<p>- Achieve monthly sales target and maintain good relationship with clients.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<p>- Working experience in related field, preferably have sales experience.</p>\n<p>- Ambitious.</p>\n<p>- Performance-oriented and sales-driven individual that fancies being remunerated generously through sheer hard-work and effort.</p>\n<p>- Independent, hardworking and highly responsible individual with a great sense of responsibility.</p>\n<p>- Passionate and driven with strong ability to self-motivate.</p>\n<p>- Excellent communication, negotiation, and interpersonal skills.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>As a Freelance Sales Executive, you’ll be responsible for identifying sales opportunities, building relationships with potential clients, and closing deals. This is a high-commission role with flexible working hours and no cap on earnings.</p>",
